  nodes:
  - editorLabel: Guard A - Forest Warning
    lines:
    - speaker: Guard
      text: Heading south into the forest? Be careful.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Guard
      text: The loggers and hunters have been reporting more monsters than usual.
        Some of them won't even go in anymore.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Guard
      text: We don't know what's causing it. Command thinks the threat is coming
        from the east, but honestly... the forest is where all the trouble is.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Guard
      text: Just watch yourself out there.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
